{"tid":1813530,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"26人涉去年十月灣仔暴動續保釋 4月再訊 控方考慮撤控禁蒙面法","createTime":"2020-01-06T10:46:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-06T10:52:16.000Z","uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"bbc3741fdf86e7fb23665f6cb7b629d2576b225d","tid":1813530,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T10:46:05.000Z","msg":"26人被控去年10月6日在灣仔參與暴動，案件押後到四月再訊，待警方進一步調查。<br />\n<br />\n全部被告繼續保釋，包括14男12女，年齡介乎13至33歲，控罪指他們在去年十月六日在灣仔軒尼詩道一帶參與暴動。<br />\n<br />\n控方指警方仍需時調查，正等候證物化驗報告，考慮到被告當中包括應屆文憑試考生，參考過應試時間表，要求法庭將案件押後至四月三日下午再提堂，獲裁判官批准。<br />\n<br />\n案中14名被告另被控違反禁蒙面法，有關條例早前被法院裁定違憲並頒令無效，政府正上訴控方代表散庭後透露，正向律政司尋求法律意見，考慮是否撤銷控罪。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=375725\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D375725&d=bwUHcV0Pscj1NrVo4Cy%2FDZbpPLVkgxcsq72qYZiHPFQ%3D&h=7c2169ac\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D375725&h=f367e31f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=375725</a>"},{"pid":"7708155d2b0d0e31e6519b414ba2b5a77401f724","tid":1813530,"uid":40839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T10:46:40.000Z","msg":"違憲有得你唔撒?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70ef7e314041734a16ba177a8d1d4cf0b58e2dff","tid":1813530,"uid":196712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T10:47:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a48feea42aabc151269660c86196dd1cabf882ef","tid":1813530,"uid":141500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T10:47:45.000Z","msg":"有咩要問律政司？ 點告一條唔存在既罪？"},{"pid":"973bcc9c236eed6b7b05f72c5c840a4a5949e292","tid":1813530,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-06T10:48:56.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n中資禍港數十年，若不肅清，真香港人恐將不復存在<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1810669\" data-auto-